        ## permission given as arguments.

        ## in directory d_xxx 
        ## a f_yyy.txt or 
        ## a directory dir_yyy
        ## are created with umask 0oxxx and
        ## permission argument 0oyyy
        ## after creating stat is used to get
        ## the actual permission of the newly
        ## created file or directory


